Directions

Dalhalla is located 7 km north of Rättvik and 280 km northwest of Stockholm. Take RV70 north from Rättvik to exit at Nittsjö/Kullsberg and follow the signs for Dalhalla.

GPS-COORDINATES

Lat N 60º 56′ 53″

Lon E 15º 6′ 13″ [/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=”1/3″][vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1607872906982{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}”]

Parking

Parking is officially open for show parking 3,5 hours before the start of a concert. We recommend arriving early to avoid traffic queues and ensure parking close to the venue. Free parking.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=”1/3″][vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1607873488916{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}”]
